{"tid":2321924,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日可唔可以一齊幫呢位手足集氣...","createTime":"2020-12-12T02:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T06:25:14.000Z","uid":10014,"like":47,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"479c40527f7573d2c231f53059852d62be095e1d","tid":2321924,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZhpW142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZhpW142.jpg&h=b2b9c966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，周五（11日）被警方加控一項「勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全」罪，成為首名被落案控告此罪名的人，更可能面臨國安公署行使管轄權送中受審。本案將於今早11時半在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n今早8時，黎智英離開荔枝角收柙，遭鐵鏈纏腰鎖手押解，猶如重犯，準備囚車押解到西九龍法院提訊。<br />\n<br />\n【被加控勾結罪　黎智英遭鐵鏈纏腰鎖手押解提堂】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2W4ytkj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2W4ytkj&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hms3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=b68810a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2W4ytkj</a><br />\n【警首引用控勾結境外危害國安　黎智英今提堂　泛民斥以言入罪】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3qNJ7dx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3qNJ7dx&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hms3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=b4e7bfd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3qNJ7dx</a><br />\n=============<br />\n📣 撐學生免費睇一年《蘋果》<br />\n學生申請：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PvsUuK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PvsUuK&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hms3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=929ea343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PvsUuK</a><br />\n=============<br />\n💪🏼 VIP撐《蘋果》計劃 每月$300起<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30DSNv1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30DSNv1&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hms3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=42d191f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30DSNv1</a><br />\n=============<br />\n🍎 黎智英：經營非常困難 請支持訂閱<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VLuV6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VLuV6g&d=gjdgNhcllS